Package: drrglm
Title: Doubly Regularized Regression for Matrix-Variate Generalized Linear Models
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2025-10-10
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Zengchao", "Xu", email="zengc.xu@aliyun.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Shan", "Luo", role="aut"),
    person("Binyan", "Jiang", role="aut"))
Maintainer: Zengchao Xu <zengc.xu@aliyun.com>
Description: 
    The doubly regularized regression for matrix-variate data solves
    a low-rank-plus-sparse structure for matrix-variate generalized 
    linear models through a weighted penalty of nuclear-norm and 
    L1-norm.
    See the paper by Xu, Luo and Jiang (2025, <doi:10.tbd>).
Depends: R (>= 4.3.0)
Imports: data.table, glmnet, Rcpp, stats
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
